==製作==
===拍攝===
導演鮑伊表示，電影正式於2016年3月10日在[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]]的[[愛丁堡|愛丁堡]]開拍<ref>{{cite news|last1=Stolworthy|first1=Jacob|title=Trainspotting 2: filming underway for Danny Boyle's long-awaited sequel|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/trainspotting-2-filming-underway-for-danny-boyles-sequel-a6925706.html|accessdate=2016-03-13|work=independent.co.uk|date=2016-03-11|archive-date=2020-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200421104754/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/trainspotting-2-filming-underway-for-danny-boyles-sequel-a6925706.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Munro|first1=Alistair|title=Shooting of Trainspotting 2 movie begins|url=http://www.edinburghnews.scotsman.com/news/shooting-of-trainspotting-2-movie-begins-1-4059303|accessdate=2016-03-13|work=Edinburgh News|date=2016-03-10|archive-date=2018-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612162713/https://www.edinburghnews.scotsman.com/news/shooting-of-trainspotting-2-movie-begins-1-4059303|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Mar2016DS">{{cite news|last1=Russell|first1=Scarlett|title=Trainspotting 2 is on! Danny Boyle starts shooting the sequel in Edinburgh|url=http://www.digitalspy.com/movies/news/a786531/trainspotting-2-danny-boyle-starts-shooting-sequel-in-edinburgh/|accessdate=2016-03-13|work=Digital Spy|date=2016-03-11|archive-date=2018-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612141506/http://www.digitalspy.com/movies/news/a786531/trainspotting-2-danny-boyle-starts-shooting-sequel-in-edinburgh/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。攝製原本預定於2016年5月進行<ref name="Mar2016DS" />。

==發行==
《猜火車2》定於2017年1月27日在英國上映，2017年2月3日排在美國發行，而世界各地則於2017年2月10日上映<ref name="Metro UK">{{cite news|last1=Lewis|first1=Rebecca|3=|title=Danny Boyle’s Trainspotting sequel finally has a name – and a release date|url=http://metro.co.uk/2016/05/16/danny-boyles-trainspotting-sequel-finally-has-a-name-and-a-release-date-5884270/|accessdate=2016-05-16|work=metro.co.uk|date=2015-05-16|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108101039/http://metro.co.uk/2016/05/16/danny-boyles-trainspotting-sequel-finally-has-a-name-and-a-release-date-5884270/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=McNary|first1=Dave|title=‘Trainspotting 2’ to Hit U.S. Theaters in February|url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/trainspotting-2-release-date-ewan-mcgregor-1201777112/|accessdate=2016-05-19|work=Variety|date=2016-05-17|archive-date=2016-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160519024315/http://variety.com/2016/film/news/trainspotting-2-release-date-ewan-mcgregor-1201777112/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《猜火車2》被選定於2017年2月的[[第67屆柏林影展|第67屆柏林影展]]上的「非競賽片」放映<ref name="Berlin">{{cite web|url=https://www.berlinale.de/en/presse/pressemitteilungen/wettbewerb/wettbewerb-presse-detail_35348.html|title=Press Releases Competition 67th Berlinale - Competition and Berlinale Special - Danny Boyle, Hong Sangsoo, Thomas Arslan, Volker Schlöndorff, Sabu, Álex de la Iglesia and Josef Hader’s Directorial Debut in the Competition Programme|work=Berlinale|date=2017-01-10|accessdate=2017-01-10|archive-date=2017-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202130800/http://www.berlinale.de/en/presse/pressemitteilungen/wettbewerb/wettbewerb-presse-detail_35348.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。美國於2017年3月17日[[有限上映|有限上映]]，3月31日起才會廣泛上映。

===評價===
《猜火車2》獲得的評價以正面居多，主要受影評人稱讚角色的情感是令人討喜，但新鮮感不如前集。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據119條評論，持有76%的新鮮度，平均得分6.8／10<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/t2_trainspotting |title=T2 Trainspotting (2017) |publisher=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2017-02-15 |archive-date=2020-04-05 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20200405172733/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/t2_trainspotting |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分64，正評居多<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/t2-trainspotting |title=T2 Trainspotting reviews |publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate=2017-01-23 |archive-date=2021-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417135405/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/t2-trainspotting |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

